Author: SemicolonButterfly
Text: Olanzapine is seriously notorious for this and for some reason my psychiatrist thought it would be fine to not mention it. Until I came back in and was like WTF and he goes, “oh, yeah, that’s common”. Yeah. He’s not my psychiatrist anymore.   (+1 for weight-neutral Latuda. -10 for my insurance not covering it.)
